invalid type: string "passage: **Loss in value and resulting loss**  \n5. We will not cover loss in value, resulting loss, or loss of use of any kind.  \n\n**Existing or deliberate damage**  \n6. We will not cover loss or damage:  \n- which occurs before cover starts or from events before cover began;  \n- caused by deliberate or malicious acts of household members, guests, tenants, or lodgers.  n